  "2026-06-26T19:05:47.605Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Evidence update: CodeFactor remediation bundle now covers the remaining duplication primitives and generated/test analysis scope. Verification passed: pnpm build; targeted 254-test suite; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm typecheck; pnpm security:scan; full coverage 100/100/100/100 across 5133 tests; manual isolated temp-project smoke with PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH passed package install/doctor and shared unset behavior. Remaining release issue #374 is external to code changes: GitHub scheduled Auto Release requires RELEASE_PAT in the release environment."
