  "2026-06-27T07:21:25.087Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Final evidence after helper cleanup: inlined the one-call cache-bust helper inside tests/unit/docs-examples/example-script-harness.ts. Current gates passed: focused docs-example tests (2/2), pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm security:scan, git diff --check, and full coverage node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 256 files / 5137 tests / 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-06-27T07:41:27.829Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Review-fix evidence: addressed Cubic/Gemini feedback on PR #385 by moving all docs-example module cache-busting through tests/unit/docs-examples/example-script-harness.ts, replacing time/random tokens with a deterministic monotonic import sequence, and consolidating starter-extension plus policy-restricted-extension example imports onto the shared harness. Updated linked docs-example test coverage now runs sdk-app-embedding, sdk-contract-consumer, starter-extension, and policy-restricted-extension specs. Gates after fix: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 256 files / 5137 tests with 100/100/100/100; pnpm lint passed with docs-example duplicates removed from jscpd output; pnpm contracts:check passed; pnpm security:scan passed; pnpm audit --audit-level low found no vulnerabilities; git diff --check passed; package doctor deep ok; pm health summary ok; history drift validation ok; Sentry critical/high 0 and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 0.72."
