  "2026-06-27T08:04:27.254Z",codex-sdk-cli-20260627,"Merge evidence: PR #385 merged to main as 753410df after final review loop on head 02500513. Current-head GitHub checks were green: Build foundation, Docs and Skills, Gates coverage/typecheck/static/compat/smokes, Runtime smoke Ubuntu Node 22/24, macOS Node 24, Windows regression Node 24, Analyze, CodeQL, CodeFactor, CodeRabbit, Hound, Sourcery, and codecov/patch. Current-head review inspection after retrigger found Gemini Code Assist reporting no review comments and no inline comments on 02500513; earlier Cubic/Gemini findings were fixed. Post-merge main verification passed: pm health summary ok, history drift validation ok, focused docs-example specs 4 files/4 tests, package doctor deep ok with pm-changelog 2026.6.27 active, and Sentry/telemetry gate critical=0 high=0 telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.72."
  "2026-06-27T17:43:53.545Z",codex-20260627-sdk-cli,"Evidence: single-sourced create/update legacy none/null collection normalization and runtime --unset field resolution; exported ConfigKey from the positional config router so config.ts no longer duplicates the canonical key union. Verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (256 files, 5137 tests, 100/100/100/100 coverage); pm test pm-92if --run --progress (7/7 linked checks passed, including Sentry/telemetry best-effort with 0 critical/high Sentry issues and telemetry ok); pnpm lint; pnpm typecheck; pnpm quality:static (duplicate_chunks=0, docstring coverage 100%); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check using pm-changelog 2026.6.27 with CHANGELOG.md unchanged; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate; pm health --check-only --summary --json ok; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift --json ok with existing resolution metadata warning backlog; package doctor deep ok; manual temp-dir smoke at /tmp/tmp.YZdcsvTxBw/work/.agents/pm passed init/config/create/update/files/docs/test/comments/close/release/health/validate. GitHub sweep found no open PRs, no Dependabot/code-scanning alerts, and issue #374 remains blocked by external RELEASE_PAT configuration."
  "2026-06-27T18:05:16.530Z",codex-20260627-sdk-cli,"Review-fix evidence: addressed Cubic P2 findings on PR #389 by scoping shared runtime --unset resolution to command_to_fields for create/update and by rejecting malformed non-string legacy none/null collection entries with a usage PmCliError. Updated helper fixtures to model command_to_fields and added a malformed payload regression test. Verification after fix passed: focused create/update/legacy-none suite (3 files, 214 tests), legacy-none focused suite (11 tests), pnpm typecheck, pnpm quality:static, pnpm lint, git diff --check, and full coverage 256 files / 5138 tests / 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-06-27T18:25:28.196Z",codex-20260627-sdk-cli,"Review evidence: addressed Gemini current-head feedback by hardening runtime unset field resolution against malformed dynamic registry fields. resolveRuntimeUnsetFieldDefinition now ignores missing/blank/non-string key, metadata_key, cli_flag, and cli_aliases entries before matching unset tokens; create-command tests cover malformed array and non-array alias metadata. Verification after this fix: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/legacy-none-tokens.spec.ts passed 3 files / 215 tests; pnpm typecheck passed; pnpm quality:static passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 256 files / 5138 tests with 100/100/100/100 coverage; pnpm lint passed; git diff --check passed."
  "2026-06-27T18:41:51.116Z",codex-20260627-sdk-cli,"Review-fix evidence: addressed current-head Cubic finding, also echoed by an older CodeRabbit thread, by normalizing runtime unset lookup tokens and all runtime field candidate forms before matching. This preserves camelCase key lookup for dynamically registered fields such as githubUrl after create/update lowercases --unset input, while keeping the malformed registry guards from the prior fix. Added create-command regression coverage for the lowercased githuburl key path. Verification after fix passed: focused create/update/legacy-none suite (3 files, 215 tests), pnpm typecheck, pnpm quality:static, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (256 files, 5138 tests, 100/100/100/100), pnpm lint, and git diff --check."
